{"id":"japho","term":"Japho","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Beauty, a sea-port in Dan (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Joshua 19:46\">Josh. 19:46</a>); called Joppa (q.v.) in <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 2:16\">2 Chr. 2:16</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 3:7\">Ezra 3:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Jonah 1:3\">Jonah 1:3</a>; and in New Testament.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Joshua 19:46","2 Chronicles 2:16","Ezra 3:7","Jonah 1:3"]}